'''1953年大西洋飓风季'''是有纪录以来第一个用事先确定的女性人名为风暴命名的大西洋飓风季，于1951年6月15日正式开始<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press]] | newspaper = The Times-News | title = Tiny Hurricane Training Medium for Observers | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YGg1AAAAIBAJ&sjid=xCMEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3873,6585368&dq=weather+bureau+hurricane+season&hl=en | archive-date = 2018-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180921074529/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YGg1AAAAIBAJ&sjid=xCMEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3873,6585368&dq=weather+bureau+hurricane+season&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，同年11月15日结束<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | date = 1953-11-14 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | accessdate = 2017-02-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0pgcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yWQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2879,3413031&dq=hurricane&hl=en | title = Hurricane Season Closes Tonight, Scores Better Than Average | archive-date = 2018-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180921074457/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0pgcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=yWQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2879,3413031&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但正式时段前后都有热带天气活动。

